OL,4,CNSPCC child abuse helpline has record
OL,5,Ccall numbers in pandemic
OL,6, Children's charity the NSPCC says calls
OL,7, and messages to its helpline have risen
OL,8, to record levels during the pandemic.
OL,10,FIn the year to March 2021 the helpline
OL,11,Fwas contacted almost 85,000 times, up
OL,12,F23% on the previous year.
OL,14,FThe figures amplify fears that children
OL,15,Fwho could not go to school during the
OL,16,Flockdowns were more vulnerable to abuse
OL,17,Fand neglect, says the NSPCC.
OL,19,FChief executive Sir Peter Wanless says
OL,20,Fgovernment recovery plans must address
OL,21,Fthe harm children may have faced.
